Mauritius Tourist Arrivals Increased by 10% Last Month, L’Express Reports

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-05-06T06:33:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/mauritius-tourist-arrivals-increased-by-10-last-month-l-express-reports.html
Mauritius attracted an estimated
64,797 tourists in April, up 10 percent from the year-earlier
period, Port Louis-based  l’Express  said, citing Karl Mootoosamy,
director of the Mauritius Tourism Promotion Authority.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in  Port Louis  via Johannesburg at 
1933 or  gbell16@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at   asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 